data.description: This beautiful corner house is located in the desirable gated Varsity Lakes Deeded Community. This community is located in a very accessible area - close to Fort Myers, RSW Airport, Lehigh Acres, a public library, schools, fine dining and more - everything you need for the Florida style living. The house and entire community has central water and sewer. There are clear well maintained sidewalks. The entire community is beautifully landscaped with several trees, flowers and fruits. The house has a screened front entryway where the lockbox is placed. At the back is an immaculate screen enclosed in ground pool. There is a huge lanai and spacious poolside area. The house has high vaulted ceilings throughout. There is a spacious living room and dining room that include an island with granite counter tops and a large eat-in kitchen. The newly upgraded appliances are immaculate and they include an indoor laundry room with washer/dryer and additional cabinets and storage area. There is a spacious master bedroom with separate tub and bath. There are also walk in closets in every bedroom.  This is a must see  house in a well maintained feel-good community.
